Problem

Churches often maintain outdated membership records, resulting in communication failures, poor engagement visibility, and inefficient follow up processes.

Solution

Developed an automated Church Member Verification System using Google Apps Script, Google Forms, and Google Sheets to improve data quality, automate follow up activities, and provide leadership reporting.

Features

Automated member verification workflow
500 record dataset generation
Executive dashboard
Ministry analysis
Attendance analysis
Follow up prioritization
Data quality monitoring
Risk register
Target operating model

Skills Demonstrated

Business Analysis
Process Improvement
Requirements Analysis
Dashboard Development
Google Apps Script
Stakeholder Reporting
Risk Management
